{"id":23,"parent_id":0,"book_id":23525,"content_id":1,"language_id":0,"display_order":23,"title":"The New Adventures of Matt and Mandy","subtitle":"","short_title":"The New Adventures of Matt and Mandy","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"article","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.head1"},["h1","The New Adventures of Matt & Mandy"]],[".bodyBlock",[".figure",{"id":"f62","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f62"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/leaders/fr13aug35-matt-and-mandy.jpg"}],[".credit",["p.para",{"id":"p2","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p2"},"Illustrations by Maryn Roos"]]],[".figure",{"id":"f63","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f63"},["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p3"},"I’ve got your science test scores here. Our new student, Mandy, is the only one who scored 100 percent."]],[".figure",{"id":"f64","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f64"},["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p4"},"If you want to make a friend, be one."]],[".figure",{"id":"f65","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f65"},["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p5"},"Hi. Your name’s Audrey, isn’t it? Is something wrong?"],["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p6"},"I flunked the test. And my dad says if I don’t get my grades up, I can’t have tennis lessons."]],[".figure",{"id":"f66","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f66"},["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p7"},"Ouch! That’s rough. Umm, listen … would you like to study together sometime? Maybe I could help."]],[".figure",{"id":"f67","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f67"},["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p8"},"You’d do that for me?"],["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p9"},"Sure. Why not?"]],[".figure",{"id":"f68","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.f68"},["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p10"},"Maybe you can teach me to play tennis. It looks fun."],["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/friend/2013/08/the-new-adventures-of-matt-and-mandy.p11"},"Yeah, I think you’d really like it."]]]]]],"refs":null}
